\end{Shaded}

\begin{verbatim}
## [1] 0.03348514
\end{verbatim}

With a correlation of 0.033, there is little to no relationship between
these two variables. There will be no further investigation of this.

\paragraph{Test correlation of Steps Vs
Sleep}\label{test-correlation-of-steps-vs-sleep}

\begin{Shaded}
